<div class="rebranding_container block-flex-wrap block-gap-50">
  <div class="rebranding-section-title block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
    <h2 class="h2-heading-ss">
      Anatomy of an 
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
        authentic Balenciaga city bag
      </span>
    </h2>
    <p class="body-text block-max-width">
      The Balenciaga City Bag is a classic design that has been popular for many years. Its unique features and high-quality materials make it a standout piece in the world of luxury handbags. Here are some key features to look for in an authentic Balenciaga City Bag:
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="article_columns-wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-start-center">
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image" src="{{ "balenciaga_anatomy-of-an-authentic-balenciaga-city-bag-1.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Relaxed, Slouchy Shape of an Authentic Balenciaga City Bag">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Relaxed, slouchy shape:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
         The bag should have a relaxed, slouchy shape, characteristic of the Balenciaga City Bag’s design.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image" src="{{ "balenciaga_anatomy-of-an-authentic-balenciaga-city-bag-2.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="High-Quality Leather of an Authentic Balenciaga City Bag">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">High-Quality leather:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The leather should be of high quality, with a soft, supple texture that feels luxurious to the touch.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image" src="{{ "balenciaga_anatomy-of-an-authentic-balenciaga-city-bag-3.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Lampo Zipper of an Authentic Balenciaga City Bag">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Lampo zipper:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The bag should have a zip closure with a Lampo zipper, ensuring smooth functionality and authenticity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image" src="{{ "balenciaga_anatomy-of-an-authentic-balenciaga-city-bag-4.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Interior Lining of an Authentic Balenciaga City Bag">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Interior lining:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The interior of the bag should be lined with high-quality fabric, such as cotton or silk, adding to the bag’s overall durability and luxury.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image" src="{{ "balenciaga_anatomy-of-an-authentic-balenciaga-city-bag-5.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Leather Tag of an Authentic Balenciaga City Bag">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Leather tag:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The bag should have a leather tag with the Balenciaga logo, a crucial element in verifying the bag’s authenticity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="body-text tac block-bottom-text w-100">
      By examining these features, you can confidently identify an authentic Balenciaga City Bag and appreciate its timeless appeal.
  </p>
</div>

